io.sphere.sdk.products

Interface Price

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Custom, PriceLike

    public interface Price
extends PriceLike
    Amount that must be paid when buying goods.

    A Price can have custom fields.

    For construction use a PriceBuilder.
    See Also:
    AddPrice, ChangePrice, RemovePrice, ProductVariant.getPrices()
